author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
Hey gang! It's time for another GMG REVIEW LIVE! Today we're checking out the latest Supplement for Joe McCullough's STARGRAVE as he explores the idea of Dominant AI in the Shattered Universe with new explorations, threats and worlds to explore in an exclusion zone considered too dangerous even by the Pirate Fleets. Let's check it out!

Check out the Let's Play for 'TEN DAYS ON LOGAN'S WORLD' HERE: https://youtu.be/Cz9_pjTw6mM

Check out the book HERE: https://www.ospreypublishing.com/us/stargrave-death-vector-9781472869159/

Music "Retrofuture Nasty" by Kevin McLeod used via Creative Commons
title: GMG Reviews - STARGRAVE - Death Vector by Joe McCullough & Osprey Games
